public class MQueryExpression
extends java.lang.Object
implements QueryExpressionDescriptor

This class is agregation of query expresion elements defined in: slee.1.1 specs chapter 10.20.2. Generaly it creates expression tree from passed arguments to match one defined in xml descriptor. This is an abstraction from plain translation from xml structure
